<view class="page"><view class="nav" style="padding-top:{{navTop}}px;height:{{navHeight}}px"><view bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}"/><text>返回课程课包</text></view></view><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height:{{navSpacer}}px"></view><view class="content"><view class="headline"><text>新建基础课包</text><text>创建标准化课程包，提升运营效率与学员体验</text></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>✎　课包名称 <text>*</text></text><text>请输入课包名称，便于识别与管理</text></view><view class="input"><input maxlength="20" placeholder="请输入课包名称" value="{{form.name}}" data-key="name" bindinput="onInput"/><text>{{form.name.length}}/20</text></view></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>♧　适用班型 <text>*</text></text><text>选择该课包适用的班级类型</text></view><picker mode="selector" range="{{classOptions}}" data-key="classType" data-source="classOptions" bindchange="onPicker"><view class="input picker"><text>{{form.classType}}</text><text wx:if="{{!form.classType}}">请选择适用班型</text><text>⌄</text></view></picker></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>¥　售价 <text>*</text></text><text>学员购买该课包的价格</text></view><view class="input unit"><text>¥</text><input type="digit" placeholder="请输入金额" value="{{form.price}}" data-key="price" bindinput="onInput"/><text>元</text></view></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>◷　总课时 <text>*</text></text><text>该课包包含的总课时数量</text></view><view class="input unit"><input type="number" placeholder="请输入课时数" value="{{form.lessons}}" data-key="lessons" bindinput="onInput"/><text>课时</text></view></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>▣　有效期 <text>*</text></text><text>课包自激活之日起的有效期限</text></view><picker mode="selector" range="{{validOptions}}" data-key="validDays" data-source="validOptions" bindchange="onPicker"><view class="input unit"><text>{{form.validDays}}</text><text>⌄　天</text></view></picker></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>▤　课消方式 <text>*</text></text><text>选择课时扣减规则</text></view><view class="choice-row"><view class="choice {{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{deductions}}" wx:key="value" data-key="deduction" data-value="{{item.value}}" bindtap="selectChoice"><text>◉　{{item.label}}</text><text>每次上课扣减固定课时</text></view></view></view>
<view class="form-card gift"><view class="field-copy"><text>♧　赠课选项</text><text>可设置赠送课时以提升吸引力</text></view><switch checked="{{giftEnabled}}" color="#ff7900" bindchange="toggleGift"/><view class="gift-box" wx:if="{{giftEnabled}}"><view><text>赠送课时</text><text>购买该课包时额外赠送的课时数</text></view><view><text>−</text><input type="number" value="{{form.giftLessons}}" data-key="giftLessons" bindinput="onInput"/><text>＋</text><text>课时</text></view></view></view>
<view class="form-card"><view class="field-copy"><text>▰　上架状态 <text>*</text></text><text>设置课包是否对学员可见并可购买</text></view><view class="choice-row"><view class="choice {{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{statuses}}" wx:key="value" data-key="status" data-value="{{item.value}}" bindtap="selectChoice"><text>◉　{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.label}}状态设置</text></view></view></view>
<view class="actions"><view bindtap="saveDraft">保存草稿</view><view bindtap="saveAndPublish">保存并上架</view></view><view class="action-notes"><text>暂不发布，保存后可继续编辑</text><text>立即发布，学员可见并可购买</text></view><view class="tip">ⓘ　复杂上架配置（价格 / 赠课 / 阶梯 / 权限等）请前往【机构PC端-课程产品】进行管理</view><view class="safe"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
